'''''sáma''''' is a [[Quenya]] word meaning "mind". The process known as ''[[ósanwë]]'' ("interchange of thought") happened between two ''samat''.<ref name=Eldarin>{{PE|Eldarin}}, p. 183</ref>

==Etymology==
[[Root]] SAM ("mind, think, reflect, be aware").<ref name=Eldarin/>

